1
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:51,080
All these weapons...

2
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,960
If you take them away,

3
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:55,240
I'm as good as dead.

4
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,960
Then do you really think

5
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,840
you'll walk out of here alive today?

6
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,360
Check it, now!

7
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,360
Sis Fei!

8
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,560
The chip is fake.

9
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,480
What?

10
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,880
Well played, Zhao Wudi.

11
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,480
How dare you trick me with a fake chip!

12
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,040
Go after them!

13
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:29,800
Yes!

14
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,080
Ma Liu!

15
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,120
Lose them!

16
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,840
No way, we can't shake them!

17
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:52,760
They're right on our tail!

18
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:53,680
Ma Liu!

19
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:54,760
Listen to me.

20
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:55,760
Get Doctor somewhere safe first.

21
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,600
Then what about you and Boss Xingyu?

22
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,280
We're the ones they're after.

23
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,640
Sticking together only makes us bigger targets.

24
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:01,800
Ma Liu.

25
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,800
Take care of Doctor.

26
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,320
Up ahead is the Death Jungle.

27
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,280
Put it there.

28
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:05,680
Stop the car!

29
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,320
We're getting out.

30
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,320
No, we can't!

31
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,440
That'd put you and Boss Xingyu in more danger.

32
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,960
If we're leaving, we leave together.

33
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,760
Old Zhang.

34
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,800
Listen to me.

35
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:15,120
Get the rare minerals back home ASAP.

36
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,480
The company's waiting.

37
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,920
This is the make-or-break moment.

38
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:19,840
This is it.

39
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,920
Up ahead is the Death Jungle.

40
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,760
Let's get out.

41
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,000
Stop!

42
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,080
Go, Xingyu!

43
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:38,880
Move!

44
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,160
Boss Xingyu!

45
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,360
Be careful!

46
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:41,800
Don't worry.

47
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,320
Careful.

48
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,320
This hellhole again.

49
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,880
Death Jungle.

50
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,760
It's usually extremely dangerous.

51
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,720
But right now,

52
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,800
there's nowhere safer than here.

53
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,280
They won't dare come in.

54
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,320
If we're in here,

55
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:30,520
it'll be hard for them to find us.

56
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,440
Go in there and you're dead.

57
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,760
How'd that punk dare go in?

58
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,200
Yeah.

59
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,560
It's terrifying.

60
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,080
Those guys,

61
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,400
none of them dare come near now.

62
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,320
Careful.

63
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,720
Wudi!

64
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,680
Where are you?

65
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,000
Wudi!

66
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,200
Shut up!

67
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,440
Stop yelling. Stop crying.

68
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,240
Let me go!

69
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:01,800
Quiet.

70
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,120
Don't move!

71
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,560
Please let me go!

72
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,640
Don't move.

73
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,280
Help me!

74
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:08,040
Don't move!

75
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:16,640
Don't be scared.

76
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,840
I'm here.

77
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,240
Go.

78
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,640
Let's go down and take a look.

79
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,160
What's wrong with you?

80
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,480
Scared the hell out of me!

81
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,680
I'm telling you,

82
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,960
I had a nightmare.

83
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,160
I dreamed...

84
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,000
Dreamed what?

85
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,440
I dreamed...

86
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:43,720
Brother Chen.

87
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,200
Brother Chen, drink up, drink up!

88
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,800
Good stuff!

89
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,800
Today I'll spare you two.

90
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,480
Go tell Hong Ye,

91
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,600
to come see me right now.

92
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,680
Okay, okay, okay!

93
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,840
Then we...

94
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,720
Hong Ye, I held them off for you.

95
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,280
You'd better protect my sister.

96
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,800
Don't disappoint me.

97
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,360
I want to go home!

98
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,200
I want to go home!

99
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,880
I want to go home!

100
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,240
I want to go home!

101
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,480
They grabbed so many kids.

102
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,360
What are they doing here?

103
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,480
Obviously,

104
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,400
it's a human trafficking base.

105
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,560
Sis Fei or Hong Ye?

106
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,040
Given how things look right now,

107
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,480
it's probably Hong Ye.

108
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:06,320
Go.

109
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,560
Let's go inside and check it out.

110
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:22,680
Ali.

111
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,760
Hey.

112
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:25,800
I took care of the guards.

113
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,600
And you're here picking up leftovers?

114
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,040
That's a bit much.

115
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,520
What are you doing here?

116
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:31,880
To kill people.

117
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,920
Am I not allowed to save people?

118
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,960
Getting you to save people must cost a fortune, huh?

119
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,520
Ms. Shen, you really get me.

120
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,720
Five million for one kid.

121
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,200
That's enough to live it up for half a year.

122
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,280
So that's why you're the Steward of Dawa.

123
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,720
Yes.

124
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,320
The small one is mine.

125
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,440
The rest,

126
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,880
they're all yours.

127
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,160
Ali...

128
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,640
Can you

129
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,920
get them all out of here?

130
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,520
I never do anything for free.

131
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,840
One million each.

132
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,080
To get them all out.

133
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,880
Two million.

134
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,120
No guarantee they'll live.

135
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,800
Five million each.

136
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,600
Get them out safely.

137
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,120
Deal.

138
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,240
You let your guard down.

139
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,360
Even though you took out the guards,

140
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:33,600
every one of them

141
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,840
was still terrified.

142
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,440
Nobody called out to us for help.

143
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,360
And

144
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,400
everyone avoided looking at him.

145
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,160
Obviously,

146
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,920
micro-expressions don't lie.

147
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,000
Looks like they found out there are

148
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,000
valuable people in here,

149
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,000
so they set up a hidden sentry.

150
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,240
Zhao Wudi,

151
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,400
I owe you a favor.

152
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,800
Let's go.

153
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,800
8317 is still inside.

154
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,200
Please, save him!

155
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,320
He was taken away.

156
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,280
That means the matching worked, got it?

157
00:08:59,320 --> 00:08:59,760
Go.

158
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,840
He's the best friend I've made

159
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,080
in here.

160
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,640
Take this doll.

161
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,280
Save him.

162
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,800
Please, save him!

163
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:11,960
This job...

164
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,400
I'll take it.

165
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:45,920
Ms. Shen.

166
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,760
Ms. Shen!

167
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,320
That startled me!

168
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,040
Why

169
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:53,240
let my two useless men

170
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,240
make you take offense?

171
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,360
If you wanted to see me,

172
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,840
you could've just called.

173
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,120
Hong Ye,

174
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,120
you're overstating it.

175
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,800
There's no taking offense here.

176
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,880
Just schooling them for you as a friend.

177
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,760
No, no, no.

178
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,520
I wouldn't dare be friends with Ms. Shen.

179
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,280
Even brothers who've followed you for over a decade,

180
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,800
you can still be ruthless to them.

181
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,560
As for Zhao Wudi,

182
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,600
he died for nothing.

183
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:20,560
You're joking again.

184
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,840
Zhao Wudi is alive and well.

185
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,840
You coming here this time

186
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,000
isn't just because I sent you

187
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,160
a message, is it?

188
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,200
Zhao Wudi and the others went in.

189
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,520
It's just a crappy little forest.

190
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,000
No need to make a big deal.

191
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:37,160
I've got plenty of business here.

192
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,400
That forest behind you is part of my business.

193
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,880
And I've stationed a lot of men here.

194
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,320
The real purpose is

195
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,920
to avoid accidentally hurting your sister.

196
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:51,720
Don't use my sister as an excuse.

197
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,480
Let's not beat around the bush.

198
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,880
I called you here this time

199
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:56,000
to make one thing clear:

200
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,720
Today, with me here,

201
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,160
you

202
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,040
and your people

203
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:01,880
aren't getting in.

204
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:06,040
Looks like today Ms. Shen

205
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,560
really wants to test

206
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:10,240
just how deep my waters run.

207
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,000
I know you can fight.

208
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,520
But what era are we in now?

209
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,560
No matter how good you are,

210
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,040
can you move faster than bullets?

211
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,840
Did you all hear me?

212
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,480
Don't disappoint Hong Ye.

213
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,360
Give her a little more excitement!

214
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,880
Cross the line and die.

215
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,440
You got my shoes all dirty.

216
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,200
Looks like today Ms. Shen

217
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,600
came well-prepared.

218
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,440
We'll meet again.

219
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,240
Xingyu.

220
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:58,840
I thought

221
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,760
this was a human trafficking place.

222
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,400
I never would've guessed

223
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:06,280
it's an illegal organ trafficking base.

224
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:09,960
Xingyu.

225
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,080
Hold your breath.

226
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,440
Xingyu!
